            <h2>The Solution</h2>
            <h3>What This Actually Is</h3>

            <p>This is <span class="highlight">production-grade lead infrastructure</span> — the routing, monitoring, and audit layer that should exist between your forms and your CRM.</p>

            <p>Built on <strong>Make.com</strong> (formerly Integromat), it's a complete event-driven system that:</p>

            <ul class="feature-list">
                <li><strong>Captures every lead</strong> at the ingress point</li>
                <li><strong>Validates and routes</strong> based on your business rules</li>
                <li><strong>Monitors every step</strong> and alerts you on failure</li>
                <li><strong>Retries failed requests</strong> automatically</li>
                <li><strong>Logs everything</strong> in an audit trail you can review months later</li>
            </ul>

            <p>It runs 24/7. It handles traffic spikes. It escalates issues before they cost you money.</p>

            <h3 style="margin-top: 64px;">What This Is NOT</h3>

            <ul class="not-list">
                <li><strong>Not a SaaS</strong> — No monthly fees, no dashboard login, no vendor lock-in</li>
                <li><strong>Not a template</strong> — This is a configured, production-ready system</li>
                <li><strong>Not a marketing funnel</strong> — This is technical infrastructure, not landing pages or email sequences</li>
            </ul>
